feboat.com/blog/2026/03/cosmic-megafauna-could-giant-alien-life-forms-exist</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 00:03:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cosmic-megafauna-could-giant-alien-life-forms-exist</guid></item><item><title>这种疗法使小鼠的寿命延长了一倍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/this-therapy-doubled-lifespan-in-mice</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 23:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/this-therapy-doubled-lifespan-in-mice</guid></item><item><title>革命性的单次注射有助于心脏病发作后的康复</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/revolutionary-single-shot-helps-with-healing-after-a-heart-attack</link><description>德克萨斯农工大学的研究人员开发出了一种单次注射疗法，可以帮助心脏病发作后的心脏恢复。心肌梗塞后，心脏会自然释放心房钠尿肽（ANP），这是一种可以减轻心脏压力并限制长期损害的激素，但数量不足。为了解决这个问题，该团队利用了自放大 RNA (saRNA) 技术：一次性肌肉注射（用标准注射器注入手臂）暂时指示肌肉细胞产生升高水平的 ANP，然后进入血液并在几周内到达心脏。在动物模型中，该治疗减少了疤痕，保留了健康的心肌，改善了泵血功能，并降低了梗塞后并发症的风险。与该团队早期的方法（例如手术植入心脏补片）相比，这种方法更简单、更实用，有可能显着改善临床工作流程和患者治疗结果。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/revolutionary-single-shot-helps-with-healing-after-a-heart-attack2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 23:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/revolutionary-single-shot-helps-with-healing-after-a-heart-attack</guid></item><item><title>独特的 TRAPP 复合物在分泌和自噬中激活 Ypt/Rab GTPases</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/distinct-trapp-complexes-activate-ypt-rab-gtpases-in-secretion-and-autophagy</link><description>保守的 Ypt1/Rab1 GTP 酶介导分泌和自噬这两个细胞过程开始的机制尚不清楚。久尔科夫斯卡等&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/distinct-trapp-complexes-activate-ypt-rab-gtpases-in-secretion-and-autophagy.gif" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 23:18:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/distinct-trapp-complexes-activate-ypt-rab-gtpases-in-secretion-and-autophagy</guid></item><item><title>通过 Atg2 在内质网-自噬体膜接触位点进行可逆单向脂质转移</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/reversible-one-way-lipid-transfer-at-er-autophagosome-membrane-contact-sites-via-atg2</link><description>李浩，铃木国典等。 （东京大学前沿科学研究生院）报告称，亲脂性染料十八烷基罗丹明 B (R18) 通过膜转移蛋白介导转运至内质网。在自噬过程中，内质网驻留的 R18 通过 Atg2 转移至自噬膜。终止后，R18 反转回 ER，表明桥式脂质转移的方向受到代谢状态的调节。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/reversible-one-way-lipid-transfer-at-er-autophagosome-membrane-contact-sites-via-atg2.gif" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 23:03:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/reversible-one-way-lipid-transfer-at-er-autophagosome-membrane-contact-sites-via-atg2</guid></item><item><title>台湾杜鹃花杜鹃（杜鹃花目，杜鹃花科）物种复合体的形态变异</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/morphological-variation-in-the-rhododendron-pseudochrysanthum-hayata-ericales-ericaceae-species-complex-from-taiwan</link><description>新的研究表明，杜鹃花 var. taitunense 是一个独特的亚种，其独特特征在于其无毛的叶子、较大的种子和特殊的花粉形态。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/morphological-variation-in-the-rhododendron-pseudochrysanthum-hayata-ericales-ericaceae-species-complex-from-taiwan2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 22:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/morphological-variation-in-the-rhododendron-pseudochrysanthum-hayata-ericales-ericaceae-species-complex-from-taiwan</guid></item></channel></rss>